      "title": "Who & What",
      "theme": "Asking about people and things",
      "intro": "The two most basic question words in Kapampangan are ninu (who) and nanu (what). Ninu asks about a person; nanu asks about an object, action, or idea. Both come at the start of the question, just like in English.",
      "wordIds": ["ask-ninu", "ask-nanu", "ask-kaninu"],
